properties.name: Super Wednesday
properties.description:
We've got a great route tonight, the greatest route, super-super luxurious. You'll be amazed. You will! Some people come up to us and they're amazed. They say, you know, "it's amazing that you can keep doing this week after week," and yes, absolutely, it is. Because we've got ideas. We've got the hugest, classiest ideas, the ideas that this city needs, and we're going to keep bringing them to you.

And you know we've only gotten started here, folks. Take tonight's ride. It's got some of the classiest alleyways around. It's got a hill  maybe not a huge hill, but that's alright, we love hills, even the little ones  and it's got some stairs that'll knock your socks off. It's gonna be a really terrific ride, just tremendous.
